---
import { Routes } from '../config/site-routing';
---

<div class="home-card-grid">
  <a class="home-card home-card--dark home-card--large" href={Routes.Knowledge}>
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>01 / KNOWLEDGE</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">知识专题</p>
      <h3>理解原理，<br />也理解边界。</h3>
      <p>按稳定的技术领域，组织经过整理和验证的长期知识。</p>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="home-card home-card--soft" href={Routes.LearningPaths}>
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>02 / PATHS</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">学习路线</p>
      <h3>从一篇笔记，<br />走向完整能力。</h3>
      <p>明确目标、前置知识与阅读顺序，让学习不再随机发生。</p>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="home-card home-card--blue" href={Routes.Retrospectives}>
    <div class="home-card-topline">
      <span>03 / RETROSPECTIVES</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="home-card-label">问题复盘</p>
      <h3>结论很重要。<br />抵达结论的过程更重要。</h3>
      <p>完整保留现象、排查、根因、方案与验证，让经验真正可复用。</p>
    </div>
  </a>
</div>

<style>
.home-card-grid {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: 1.28fr 0.72fr;
	gap: 1.25rem;
}

.home-card {
	position: relative;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	justify-content: space-between;
	min-height: 34rem;
	padding: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
	border: 0;
	border-radius: 2rem;
	overflow: hidden;
	text-decoration: none;
	box-shadow: none;
	transition: transform 320ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1), box-shadow 320ms ease;
}

.home-card:hover {
	transform: translateY(-5px);
	box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.home-card:focus-visible {
	outline: 3px solid #0071e3;
	outline-offset: 4px;
}

.home-card-topline {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: space-between;
	font-size: 0.7rem;
	font-weight: 700;
	letter-spacing: 0.12em;
	opacity: 0.72;
}

.home-card-topline span:last-child {
	font-size: 1.15rem;
	font-weight: 400;
	letter-spacing: 0;
	transition: transform 240ms ease;
}

.home-card:hover .home-card-topline span:last-child {
	transform: translate(3px, -3px);
}

.home-card-label {
	margin-bottom: 1rem !important;
	font-size: 0.9rem;
	font-weight: 600;
	opacity: 0.74;
}

.home-card h3 {
	max-width: 10ch;
	font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.8vw, 4.7rem);
	font-weight: 620;
	line-height: 0.98;
	letter-spacing: -0.06em;
}

.home-card > div:last-child > p:last-child {
	max-width: 34rem;
	margin-top: 1.7rem;
	font-size: 1.04rem;
	line-height: 1.5;
	opacity: 0.7;
}

.home-card--dark {
	color: #f5f5f7;
	background:
		radial-gradient(circle at 84% 18%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14), transparent 15rem),
		#000000;
}

.home-card--dark :is(h3, p, span),
.home-card--blue :is(h3, p, span) {
	color: inherit;
}

.home-card--soft {
	color: #1d1d1f;
	background: #f5f5f7;
}

.home-card--soft h3 {
	font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 3.9rem);
}

.home-card--blue {
	grid-column: 1 / -1;
	min-height: 31rem;
	color: #ffffff;
	background:
		radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), transparent 19rem),
		linear-gradient(145deg, #0071e3 0%, #0062c4 100%);
}

.home-card--blue h3 {
	max-width: 13ch;
}

:global(:root[data-theme='dark']) .home-card--soft {
	color: #f5f5f7;
	background: #1c1c1e;
}

@media (max-width: 50rem) {
	.home-card-grid {
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
	}

	.home-card,
	.home-card--blue {
		grid-column: auto;
		min-height: 29rem;
		border-radius: 1.6rem;
	}

	.home-card h3,
	.home-card--soft h3 {
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 11vw, 3.7rem);
	}
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
	.home-card,
	.home-card-topline span:last-child {
		transition: none;
	}
}

.home-card--dark {
	background:
		radial-gradient(circle at 84% 18%, rgba(255, 254, 242, 0.12), transparent 15rem),
		var(--home-ink);
}

.home-card--soft,
:global(:root[data-theme='dark']) .home-card--soft {
	color: var(--home-ink);
	background: var(--home-paper-deep);
}

.home-card--blue {
	background:
		radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, rgba(255, 254, 242, 0.18), transparent 19rem),
		linear-gradient(145deg, #315a45 0%, var(--home-green) 100%);
}
</style>
